{"tid":1469359,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非要同勇武派割蓆","createTime":"2019-08-14T01:33:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T01:42:14.000Z","uid":223518,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"66e3c58639c24c7bb3fee34845dc2bba9e460d96","tid":1469359,"uid":223518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:33:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">一條毛都唔會割</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">手足</span></span></span>(和理非同勇武派)再好似琴日機場咁,意見有好&times;大差距時,我地只會消耗手足的體力,結果唔會令我地更團結或更有作為,這是<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">兄弟爬山的缺點</span></span>,也令我們必須去<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">正視這問題</span></span>的關口。<br />\n<br />\n又在種種原因下,我們強調<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">現場決定</span></span>,即使在示威中,兵慌馬亂的情況下,勇武派在也能在<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">前線討論</span></span>,為現場的行動<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">作出共識</span></span>,引證我們每場示威,都需要<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">短暫的行動討論台</span></span>,務求盡快為現場的行動達到<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">共識</span></span>,作出有效的行動,發揮人多的效用,消除兄弟爬山的缺點。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>We need to talk<br />\nWe need to talk<br />\nWe need to talk</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望手足的<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">意見有大差異時</span></span>,有一個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>共識</strong></span></span>。<br />\n  聽到<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">We need to talk</span></strong></span>,立即圍繞在有問題的地方/事情,並且以出現問題的地方/事情為中心,<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">製造一個穩定的環境</span></span>,<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">展開</span></span>有效的<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">討論</span></span>,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點x樣</span></span>令環境穩定呀,琴晚機場都好x亂啦！<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點x樣</span></span>展開有效的討論呀？<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>個環境好x亂呀!</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我都唔x知</span></span>,但為左事情可以繼續前進,<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">為左我地可以繼續前進</span></span>,我地必須在<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">沒有大台的情況下</span></span>,<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">突破兄弟爬山的缺點</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n我個人提出,為現場緊急討論名為 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>示公會議</strong></span></span>(示威者公開會議) , 會議除左唔同意所有胡亂謾罵和胡作非為的人外,沒有任何限制,<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">一切由</span></span>最<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">接近問題根源</span></span>的<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">現場人士決定</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n重申,希望手足有個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">共識</span></strong></span>,一聽到<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">We need to talk</span></strong></span>,不論和理非定勇武派,立即製造穩定的環境,為行動作出有效的討論。<br />\n<br />\n和理非和勇武能時常<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">達到共識</span></span>,我地先有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">更大力量</span></span>去行動,一切為左 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>光復香港 時代革命</strong></span></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry